A vintage-style illustration of a warm, cozy study desk at dawn on January 1st, viewed from above. Scattered across the worn wooden surface: an open leather journal with handwritten lists, a steaming cup of tea, a small globe showing Southeast Asia, dancing shoes, dumbbells, and programming books stacked haphazardly. A window reveals fireworks fading in a pink-orange sunrise sky over a tropical cityscape with palm trees. Family photographs in ornate frames are propped against the wall. The color palette is warm sepia tones with pops of festive gold and deep burgundy, evoking hopeful nostalgia and quiet determination for the year ahead.
